    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下教育平台的组件依赖关系。核心是GradeSync成绩同步模块，它会被多个客户端使用，包括命令行工具、桌面应用和后台API服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomApi",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那SDK和Lib的定位是什么？我理解为SDK是统一对外暴露的门户，Lib是内部共享的基础库，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。CustomSDK对接Education_LMS_Portal门户，所有客户端都通过SDK间接使用Lib。另外SDK和API之间是HTTP连接，需要标注清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomApi",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出五个核心类：CLI工具、桌面应用、API服务、SDK和Lib，标注好各自的业务域。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CLI工具这里要注意，它除了调用SDK，还会直接依赖Lib处理Education_ContentCDN的内容分发逻辑，这个依赖关系别漏了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomLib",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加CLI到Lib的using关系。那SDK到API的通信细节需要展开吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要。SDK向API发送bRequest消息，业务场景是Education_GradeSync；API返回bResponse消息，数据源是Education_StudentDB。这两个消息流要分开画。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi",
        "bRequest",
        "bResponse",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，SDK到API用实线箭头标bRequest，返回用虚线箭头标bResponse。另外我把HTTP连接标注为斜体，放在旁边。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi",
        "bRequest",
        "bResponse",
        "HTTP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
