      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，API服务本身也会直接调用Lib对吧？还有桌面应用也是既用SDK也用Lib？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomSdk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：API到Lib是using关系，桌面应用到Lib也是using关系，桌面应用到SDK也是using关系。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomSdk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。还有SDK到Lib的using关系也别忘了，这是核心依赖。整体方向建议从左到右，CLI和App在左，SDK居中，API和Lib在右侧。",
